# ğŸ“š Chat-IHEC â€“ Chat with Your Documents

An intelligent chatbot app powered by **LangChain**, **Ollama**, and **FAISS** that lets you:

- Upload `.pdf` or `.txt` files
- Ask questions about their content
- Get answers in **French or English automatically**
- See which parts of the documents were used to generate each answer
- Stream answers in real-time like ChatGPT

